275
00:18:38,633 --> 00:18:39,963
- Yes. - Sin Won.

276
00:18:40,963 --> 00:18:42,343
What? What is it?

277
00:18:42,443 --> 00:18:43,263
Does something hurt?

278
00:18:43,663 --> 00:18:44,693
You don't look good.

279
00:18:46,133 --> 00:18:46,823
Banjju.

280
00:18:47,423 --> 00:18:49,153
Are you finally worried about me?

281
00:18:49,653 --> 00:18:51,853
I ask because you look uglier than usual,

282
00:18:52,053 --> 00:18:53,243
leader Kim Sin Won.

283
00:18:53,543 --> 00:18:54,813
I knew it. You bastard.

284
00:18:56,363 --> 00:18:58,773
Why is it pulsating so much?

285
00:18:59,573 --> 00:19:01,553
The opening is approaching.

286
00:19:02,053 --> 00:19:03,833
You must feel the pressure.

287
00:19:04,433 --> 00:19:05,483
I'm fine.

288
00:19:05,583 --> 00:19:07,503
If it is successful, everything will be fine.

289
00:19:09,063 --> 00:19:11,753
I rely on you until the end.

290
00:19:12,453 --> 00:19:13,163
Any.

291
00:19:17,173 --> 00:19:17,913
Su Jeong.

292
00:19:23,163 --> 00:19:24,153
Director Ban,

293
00:19:25,153 --> 00:19:28,323
You look much happier than when you're with me.

294
00:19:29,023 --> 00:19:30,473
Of course, it's not the same.

295
00:19:30,573 --> 00:19:32,053
Do you openly discriminate?

296
00:19:32,153 --> 00:19:33,113
What do you mean?

297
00:19:33,213 --> 00:19:34,823
You are Mrs. Kwon...

298
00:19:35,823 --> 00:19:37,483
and Su Jeong is simply Su Jeong.

299
00:19:40,273 --> 00:19:41,223
This is not correct.

300
00:19:42,223 --> 00:19:44,843
I'll start bringing you espresso starting tomorrow.

301
00:19:44,943 --> 00:19:45,983
with a triple dose.

302
00:19:47,183 --> 00:19:48,833
Will you accept my apology?

303
00:19:48,933 --> 00:19:50,173
No, I won't accept.

304
00:19:51,273 --> 00:19:52,563
Because I was joking.

305
00:19:53,163 --> 00:19:54,133
Enjoy your date.

306
00:19:56,353 --> 00:19:58,353
Thanks to you, I have more free time.

307
00:19:58,553 --> 00:19:59,103
Thank you.

308
00:19:59,903 --> 00:20:00,503
Any.

309
00:20:04,533 --> 00:20:06,693
Manager Kwon has a sense of humor.

310
00:20:06,793 --> 00:20:08,183
It just dawned on me now.

311
00:20:10,103 --> 00:20:11,353
I am grateful to her for that.

312
00:20:13,443 --> 00:20:14,833
This is for the Black Dragon.

313
00:20:14,933 --> 00:20:16,623
This is for Strawberry.

314
00:20:17,523 --> 00:20:18,463
Ha Jin.

315
00:20:19,163 --> 00:20:21,073
I'm glad to see you sitting next to each other.

316
00:20:21,673 --> 00:20:23,973
Is Leader Kim feeling better?

317
00:20:24,573 --> 00:20:26,383
What? Is he sick?

318
00:20:28,373 --> 00:20:29,533
What? You didn't know that?

319
00:20:29,733 --> 00:20:31,663
Ide o to...

320
00:20:35,843 --> 00:20:37,453
Did you have a fight?

321
00:20:37,853 --> 00:20:38,733
They didn't argue.

322
00:20:40,363 --> 00:20:41,373
Well, just...

323
00:20:41,473 --> 00:20:44,383
Did he annoy you by smiling at everyone?

324
00:20:44,483 --> 00:20:46,483
No, he didn't get angry.

325
00:20:46,983 --> 00:20:49,963
I'm the one who made him angry.

326
00:20:50,463 --> 00:20:53,743
I'm the one who couldn't love him the way he wanted,

327
00:20:53,843 --> 00:20:56,103
nor allow him to love me.

328
00:20:56,803 --> 00:20:58,953
I thought I was fine after the divorce,

329
00:20:59,053 --> 00:21:02,783
but probably not enough to completely trust anyone.

330
00:21:03,883 --> 00:21:05,963
Of course you're afraid.

331
00:21:06,363 --> 00:21:08,623
After all, someone you trusted the most has changed.

332
00:21:10,143 --> 00:21:13,923
But if you want to trust him,

333
00:21:14,423 --> 00:21:16,913
Doesn't that mean you love him that much?

334
00:21:20,023 --> 00:21:21,493
Even if you're afraid,

335
00:21:22,193 --> 00:21:23,993
You want to believe in love.

336
00:21:36,823 --> 00:21:38,253
Thanks for the ride home.

337
00:21:38,353 --> 00:21:39,783
You're going straight home, right?

338
00:21:39,983 --> 00:21:41,403
I'll stop by at work.

339
00:21:41,603 --> 00:21:42,603
What for?

340
00:21:43,103 --> 00:21:45,983
I have a meeting with Arteta's headquarters via video call.

341
00:21:46,683 --> 00:21:48,923
I thought you already made a deal with them.

342
00:21:49,123 --> 00:21:50,653
I wanted to check a few things.

343
00:21:50,753 --> 00:21:52,423
I can't afford even a small mistake.

344
00:21:52,523 --> 00:21:54,433
for the success of the project.

345
00:21:55,433 --> 00:21:57,663
Don't feel too pressured.

346
00:21:57,763 --> 00:21:59,523
We work hard together.

347
00:21:59,723 --> 00:22:00,383
Okay?

348
00:22:04,713 --> 00:22:05,813
Go ahead.

349
00:22:05,913 --> 00:22:07,843
I'll watch you go in.

350
00:22:08,043 --> 00:22:09,953
No, I want to see you leave.

351
00:23:10,783 --> 00:23:12,503
You came early.

352
00:23:12,603 --> 00:23:15,623
Yes. My supervisor encouraged me to update the design,

353
00:23:15,723 --> 00:23:19,333
so that I don't fall into depression.

354
00:23:20,763 --> 00:23:22,403
He said he had been working in the office all night.

355
00:23:22,503 --> 00:23:24,693
So I really can't complain.

356
00:23:25,093 --> 00:23:27,003
Did he work all night in the office?

357
00:23:27,103 --> 00:23:27,773
Yes.

358
00:23:30,093 --> 00:23:31,853
Is he at home now?

359
00:23:31,953 --> 00:23:33,413
He left for a meeting with the company.

360
00:23:33,513 --> 00:23:35,143
He will check the place there too.

361
00:23:35,243 --> 00:23:36,523
Is he checking the place again?

362
00:23:36,623 --> 00:23:38,633
We recently checked it out together.

363
00:23:38,733 --> 00:23:40,083
We'll check it again the day before.

364
00:23:40,183 --> 00:23:41,473
You know how thorough he is.

365
00:23:41,573 --> 00:23:42,573
Well then...

366
00:23:57,943 --> 00:23:59,593
Didn't you go home last night?

367
00:24:00,093 --> 00:24:02,763
I lost track of time while working.

368
00:24:02,863 --> 00:24:04,553
When are you returning to the office?

369
00:24:04,653 --> 00:24:06,533
I'll pick you up when you're done.

370
00:24:08,003 --> 00:24:10,993
The restoration project must be successful.

371
00:24:11,093 --> 00:24:13,803
If it fails, we will have to leave the company.

372
00:24:22,603 --> 00:24:23,733
Manager Kwon.

373
00:24:27,673 --> 00:24:30,193
I can't help but find it strange.

374
00:24:30,293 --> 00:24:32,353
We are almost ready to open.

375
00:24:32,453 --> 00:24:35,153
He shouldn't have so much work.

376
00:24:35,453 --> 00:24:37,353
But it is overworked.

377
00:24:37,553 --> 00:24:39,103
He must be worried.

378
00:24:39,703 --> 00:24:43,333
Because he would lose everything if it didn't work out.

379
00:24:44,333 --> 00:24:46,873
What do you mean?

380
00:24:56,406 --> 00:24:57,276
Director of the Bank.

381
00:24:59,890 --> 00:25:01,430
What are you doing here, Su Jeong...

382
00:25:05,145 --> 00:25:06,435
Is everything okay?

383
00:25:07,135 --> 00:25:08,315
I heard,

384
00:25:10,125 --> 00:25:12,465
that if it doesn't work out, you don't just quit.

385
00:25:13,165 --> 00:25:15,395
You agreed to give up your property, your name

386
00:25:15,595 --> 00:25:17,405
and you will leave the country.

387
00:25:17,605 --> 00:25:20,045
Why did you agree to such an exaggerated condition?

388
00:25:20,645 --> 00:25:21,405
I wanted to...

389
00:25:24,385 --> 00:25:27,285
leave the decision up to you.

390
00:25:27,885 --> 00:25:29,485
I wanted you to choose,

391
00:25:30,485 --> 00:25:32,375
whether you stay in the company or not.

392
00:25:33,345 --> 00:25:35,705
I didn't try to get a job.

393
00:25:36,205 --> 00:25:37,055
Why is this for me...

394
00:25:37,155 --> 00:25:39,015
I know. You did it for me.

395
00:25:39,515 --> 00:25:41,695
You wanted my grandmother to recognize me.

396
00:25:41,995 --> 00:25:45,105
and she didn't let my life's work go to waste.

397
00:25:45,805 --> 00:25:48,565
Did you decide that even though you knew?

398
00:25:49,165 --> 00:25:51,265
Because I can give up everything.

399
00:25:54,425 --> 00:25:56,585
If I can be greedy for once,

400
00:25:58,845 --> 00:26:00,475
It must be because of you, Baek Su Jeong.

401
00:26:02,455 --> 00:26:03,925
All I cared about was...

402
00:26:05,585 --> 00:26:07,925
to have your efforts recognized.

403
00:26:09,515 --> 00:26:10,485
Because I know,

404
00:26:12,575 --> 00:26:14,775
how desperately you want it.

405
00:26:20,175 --> 00:26:21,345
Because I also know,

406
00:26:22,775 --> 00:26:25,175
what it's like to want recognition.

407
00:26:25,775 --> 00:26:28,295
And the person I really want to appreciate me,

408
00:26:31,255 --> 00:26:32,945
is right in front of me right now.

409
00:26:38,595 --> 00:26:40,335
I'm sorry I didn't tell you.

410
00:26:45,685 --> 00:26:47,095
Can you come here for a moment?

411
00:26:55,575 --> 00:26:57,345
You wanted to learn to play the piano.

412
00:26:58,755 --> 00:27:00,005
Do you remember?

413
00:27:00,905 --> 00:27:02,705
When did I want to learn...

414
00:27:04,945 --> 00:27:06,775
I have piano class in the afternoon.

415
00:27:06,875 --> 00:27:08,045
I have time off after five.

416
00:27:08,145 --> 00:27:09,795
Wow, amazing.

417
00:27:09,895 --> 00:27:10,965
Do you take piano lessons?

418
00:27:11,065 --> 00:27:12,825
I've always wanted to learn it too.

419
00:27:13,225 --> 00:27:15,455
You can learn from me later.

420
00:27:19,615 --> 00:27:22,755
Honestly, I still can't believe it.

421
00:27:23,255 --> 00:27:25,075
That we met again

422
00:27:25,775 --> 00:27:28,205
and we fell in love.

423
00:27:28,705 --> 00:27:31,015
So I couldn't think of anything else.

424
00:27:34,575 --> 00:27:36,495
Don't try to do everything yourself.

425
00:27:38,955 --> 00:27:40,345
I will never do that again.

426
00:27:44,315 --> 00:27:46,275
I haven't stopped being angry yet.

427
00:27:48,515 --> 00:27:49,785
I think so already.

428
00:28:07,845 --> 00:28:09,731
GRACE

429
00:28:15,085 --> 00:28:18,315
But if you want to believe him,

430
00:28:18,915 --> 00:28:20,975
Doesn't that mean you love him that much?

431
00:28:25,815 --> 00:28:27,445
Really, that handsome employee.

432
00:28:27,645 --> 00:28:29,165
I haven't seen him lately.

433
00:28:29,365 --> 00:28:30,725
Is it finished?

434
00:28:32,225 --> 00:28:34,715
He wasn't an employee. He was just helping me out for a short time.

435
00:28:35,615 --> 00:28:37,805
Why? Are you sad?

436
00:28:38,205 --> 00:28:39,515
No, I'm not.

437
00:28:39,615 --> 00:28:42,285
He was nicer to the owner than to the customers.

438
00:28:42,885 --> 00:28:45,725
He's your boyfriend, right?

439
00:28:46,125 --> 00:28:47,815
Why are you asking that?

440
00:28:48,315 --> 00:28:49,895
What? I'm curious.

441
00:28:49,995 --> 00:28:51,995
Don't ask questions. It's rude.

442
00:29:07,585 --> 00:29:10,225
It's lunchtime, team leader.

443
00:29:12,195 --> 00:29:12,945
Okay.

444
00:29:13,345 --> 00:29:15,255
You haven't changed at all.

445
00:29:15,455 --> 00:29:17,955
Director Ban is your friend. Why are you working so hard?

446
00:29:19,835 --> 00:29:21,585
Can't we have steak today?

447
00:29:22,285 --> 00:29:23,875
Director Ban is in the department store.

448
00:29:23,975 --> 00:29:25,515
And I have a meeting with someone.

449
00:29:26,975 --> 00:29:28,775
You have a meeting with Manager Kim Hee Jeong.

450
00:29:29,075 --> 00:29:30,835
I thought he worked in America.

451
00:29:31,235 --> 00:29:32,895
He's working. He's in Big Forest.

452
00:29:32,995 --> 00:29:34,735
He's in Korea for a while.

453
00:29:35,735 --> 00:29:38,195
Isn't Big Forest the largest shopping mall in America?

454
00:29:38,295 --> 00:29:39,315
Yes, it is.

455
00:29:39,615 --> 00:29:40,835
But I didn't think so.

456
00:29:41,035 --> 00:29:43,355
that you are close enough to meet.

457
00:29:44,055 --> 00:29:45,575
Does he by any chance want to hire you?

458
00:29:46,375 --> 00:29:48,015
Come on. No way.

459
00:29:49,965 --> 00:29:51,035
You're right.

460
00:29:52,635 --> 00:29:53,645
I want to hire you.

461
00:29:55,625 --> 00:29:58,025
We only worked together briefly,

462
00:29:58,525 --> 00:30:01,335
but even though you were a rookie, you excelled.

463
00:30:01,435 --> 00:30:04,785
I'm following the news from Korea, but...

464
00:30:05,985 --> 00:30:08,495
I understand why you were promoted so quickly.

465
00:30:09,995 --> 00:30:12,315
Thank you for having such a high opinion of me.

466
00:30:13,415 --> 00:30:14,455
I heard about the scandal.

467
00:30:14,555 --> 00:30:17,055
and also about how you were transferred for a while.

468
00:30:19,565 --> 00:30:21,225
If you stay in Yongsung,

469
00:30:21,725 --> 00:30:24,375
they will continue to treat you this badly.

470
00:30:24,875 --> 00:30:28,005
You'll just be Ban Ju Yeon's boyfriend.

471
00:30:28,705 --> 00:30:32,115
You wouldn't give up your career for love, would you?

472
00:30:32,815 --> 00:30:34,175
That would be a shame.

473
00:30:34,375 --> 00:30:37,025
All your hard work would go to waste.

474
00:30:38,485 --> 00:30:39,765
So...

475
00:30:41,225 --> 00:30:42,555
come to America.

476
00:30:46,355 --> 00:30:48,825
I really appreciate your offer,

477
00:30:49,425 --> 00:30:51,955
but right now I'm working on a project.

478
00:30:55,155 --> 00:30:59,035
I even appreciate your sense of responsibility.

479
00:31:01,355 --> 00:31:02,135
Okay.

480
00:31:02,835 --> 00:31:04,955
Don't rush.

481
00:31:05,055 --> 00:31:07,195
and we'll talk again after the project.

482
00:31:38,695 --> 00:31:40,515
Mama!

483
00:31:41,115 --> 00:31:41,815
Su Hyeok!

484
00:31:45,635 --> 00:31:46,665
Are you crazy?

485
00:31:46,765 --> 00:31:48,345
How could you push a child?

486
00:31:48,945 --> 00:31:50,535
I didn't push him. I held him back.

487
00:31:50,635 --> 00:31:53,175
He almost ran into someone while running.

488
00:31:54,505 --> 00:31:55,825
Ban Ju-yeon?

489
00:32:03,365 --> 00:32:05,975
Yes, I saw you on the news.

490
00:32:06,575 --> 00:32:08,245
You could have said something to him.

491
00:32:08,345 --> 00:32:11,345
Can you reach for my precious child if you are rich?

492
00:32:13,655 --> 00:32:15,605
Sorry I scared him.

493
00:32:15,705 --> 00:32:17,415
But it was an emergency.

494
00:32:17,515 --> 00:32:19,995
If you want, you can watch the camera footage.

495
00:32:25,425 --> 00:32:26,265
Team leader,

496
00:32:26,865 --> 00:32:28,275
you have to see this.

497
00:32:28,875 --> 00:32:31,005
Yongsung's successor,

498
00:32:31,105 --> 00:32:32,885
who is known for being young and handsome,

499
00:32:32,985 --> 00:32:34,715
in the restaurant section of the department store

500
00:32:34,815 --> 00:32:37,325
He pushed the little boy and knocked him to the ground.

501
00:32:37,425 --> 00:32:41,395
Apparently just because he was in his way. Wow.

502
00:32:41,495 --> 00:32:43,365
- That's not possible. - It seems...

503
00:32:43,465 --> 00:32:46,815
that Yongsung plans after the renovation

504
00:32:46,915 --> 00:32:51,455
to turn the luxury wing into a child-free zone.

505
00:32:51,555 --> 00:32:53,645
How can a department store prohibit children from entering?

506
00:32:53,745 --> 00:32:55,825
We need to report this asshole.

507
00:32:55,925 --> 00:32:57,425
Send me the link immediately.

508
00:32:57,625 --> 00:32:58,205
Okay.

509
00:33:00,115 --> 00:33:03,155
Edited customer posts on social media

510
00:33:03,255 --> 00:33:05,015
with malicious intent.

511
00:33:05,115 --> 00:33:08,095
They're speculating that you've been fired.

512
00:33:08,195 --> 00:33:09,965
because of a bad reputation.

513
00:33:10,065 --> 00:33:11,885
Public opinion is very negative.

514
00:33:12,285 --> 00:33:14,675
They even mention a boycott.

515
00:33:15,175 --> 00:33:17,155
Things will calm down in time.

516
00:33:17,255 --> 00:33:20,395
Let's say we take strong action against fake news.

517
00:33:20,495 --> 00:33:22,055
Sure, but...

518
00:33:22,655 --> 00:33:24,185
regarding timing,

519
00:33:24,285 --> 00:33:28,355
I'm worried it will affect the reopening.

520
00:33:28,755 --> 00:33:30,815
First, find the person who posted the video.

521
00:33:31,015 --> 00:33:31,925
It's on...

522
00:33:33,225 --> 00:33:34,576
something suspicious.

523
00:33:35,500 --> 00:33:38,330
YONGSUNG FACES INSPECTION BEFORE REOPENING

524
00:33:41,165 --> 00:33:42,205
Representative Yang,

525
00:33:42,505 --> 00:33:44,685
The performer wants to cancel the performance.

526
00:33:44,785 --> 00:33:46,495
to celebrate the reopening.

527
00:33:48,645 --> 00:33:50,615
God, he's going to beat me.

528
00:33:50,715 --> 00:33:52,685
Reopening is just around the corner.

529
00:34:00,905 --> 00:34:01,805
Team leader,

530
00:34:02,105 --> 00:34:04,785
The performance at the Botanical House will not take place.

531
00:34:07,685 --> 00:34:10,005
Yes, team leader. I'm on my way.

532
00:34:10,105 --> 00:34:11,125
I don't know how to say it.

533
00:34:11,225 --> 00:34:12,615
I'm sorry,

534
00:34:12,715 --> 00:34:15,065
but we have to cancel today's meeting.

535
00:34:15,165 --> 00:34:18,025
- Excuse me? - The author learned about the gossip.

536
00:34:18,125 --> 00:34:20,755
"The Pirate King" is an animated film for children.

537
00:34:20,855 --> 00:34:22,625
He said the booth couldn't be set up there,

538
00:34:22,725 --> 00:34:24,955
where they are not kind to children.

539
00:34:25,855 --> 00:34:27,435
It's a misunderstanding.

540
00:34:27,835 --> 00:34:29,895
I can send you evidence that proves this.

541
00:34:29,995 --> 00:34:32,805
I will send you an email regarding the cancellation of the contract.

542
00:34:32,905 --> 00:34:34,365
The opening is in three days.

543
00:34:34,465 --> 00:34:36,385
This is not right, team leader.

544
00:34:36,485 --> 00:34:37,835
I'm sorry.

545
00:34:43,655 --> 00:34:47,525
"The Pirate King" is an exceptional animated film for me.

546
00:35:13,175 --> 00:35:15,025
Yes, that's me.

547
00:35:16,755 --> 00:35:17,805
Black dragon.

548
00:35:43,175 --> 00:35:45,285
We will finally meet him in person.

549
00:35:45,685 --> 00:35:50,155
