823
00:55:40,350 --> 00:55:42,030
I told you so.

824
00:55:42,330 --> 00:55:44,630
Staying in Yongsung has its limits.

825
00:55:44,930 --> 00:55:46,270
Think about it.

826
00:55:46,870 --> 00:55:48,980
and let me know by the end of the month.

827
00:55:53,550 --> 00:55:55,602
THANK YOU.

828
00:56:06,670 --> 00:56:08,210
THE YOUNG HEIR IS A ROMANTIC

829
00:56:08,310 --> 00:56:10,836
STAND OF THE POPULAR ANIMATION THE PIRATE KING...

830
00:56:18,360 --> 00:56:20,130
I made sure that Miss Baek's personal information

831
00:56:20,230 --> 00:56:21,760
will not be published.

832
00:56:22,160 --> 00:56:25,140
But it's hard to remove posts,

833
00:56:25,440 --> 00:56:27,360
which are already on social media.

834
00:56:28,060 --> 00:56:29,430
There's nothing you can do about it.

835
00:56:30,700 --> 00:56:32,800
Thank you for everything. You can go home.

836
00:56:33,100 --> 00:56:36,450
Go home too. It's late.

837
00:56:36,550 --> 00:56:37,420
Any.

838
00:57:02,620 --> 00:57:03,630
Have you been waiting long?

839
00:57:04,130 --> 00:57:04,930
Three minutes?

840
00:57:05,430 --> 00:57:06,480
- Let's go. - Okay.

841
00:57:07,680 --> 00:57:09,840
Wow, it's Christmas already.

842
00:57:10,340 --> 00:57:13,990
Do you remember how we hunted together in "Legend" at Christmas?

843
00:57:14,490 --> 00:57:17,230
Sure. We also had the same clothes.

844
00:57:18,430 --> 00:57:19,750
It was fun.

845
00:57:22,130 --> 00:57:24,390
We've already spent time together.

846
00:57:24,490 --> 00:57:26,550
also Christmas and New Year.

847
00:57:27,750 --> 00:57:30,460
Even though this is our first Christmas holding hands.

848
00:57:34,940 --> 00:57:36,360
Those journalists today...

849
00:57:37,660 --> 00:57:38,780
That's okay.

850
00:57:39,280 --> 00:57:41,830
I was just surprised that they rushed at me like that.

851
00:57:43,600 --> 00:57:46,050
- I... - You mustn't apologize.

852
00:57:46,650 --> 00:57:48,700
Don't even blame yourself.

853
00:57:50,110 --> 00:57:52,450
If I were in their place, I would be interested too.

854
00:57:53,050 --> 00:57:55,260
I would like to know who you are dating.

855
00:57:56,700 --> 00:57:57,530
Really?

856
00:57:58,430 --> 00:57:59,600
Clearly.

857
00:58:02,310 --> 00:58:03,130
Su Jeong.

858
00:58:13,930 --> 00:58:15,320
If you want, then leave.

859
00:58:18,650 --> 00:58:20,240
Okay, tomorrow.

860
00:58:35,430 --> 00:58:38,150
MY DEAREST NEMEZIS